title: Close Encounters of the 5th Kind: Origins
body:
In the first episode of this enlightening 10-part special, Dr. Steven Greer discusses the major life events which unlocked his innate abilities to connect with extraterrestrials. Inspired by his contact with ETs, Dr. Greer developed the CE5 Protocols using consciousness, remote viewing, and coherent thought sequencing. Dr. Greer now champions a global community that empowers individuals to establish direct contact with extraterrestrial intelligences. 

In the next episode, Dr. Greer reveals his catalysts for extraterrestrial contact.

Dr. Steven Greer is the founding father of the Disclosure Project, The Center for the Study of Extraterrestrial Intelligence, and creator of the CE5 Contact protocol.

title: Catalysts for Contact
body:
Dr. Steven Greer dives deeper into his journey of ET discovery and Disclosure. A direct extraterrestrial contact and synchronistic life-defining events in the summer of 1990, served as the catalyst for his founding of The Center for The Study of Extraterrestrial Intelligence (CSETI). His mission was revealed — to facilitate ET contact and join a community of peaceful intergalactic civilizations. 

In the next episode, gain a deeper view of the Disclosure movement.

Dr. Steven Greer is the founding father of the Disclosure Project, The Center for the Study of Extraterrestrial Intelligence, and creator of the CE5 Contact protocol.

title: Project Starlight
body:
The disclosure movement has been building for the past 30 years. In the early 1990s, as Dr. Steven Greer began to learn more about the multiple levels of secrecy within US government and military, he founded Project Starlight to bring knowledge of ET activity to light. With the help of information from high-ranking insiders, he was able to collect a strong database of evidence to the presence of ET technology and communication known within government organizations. He continues to inspire public action to connect directly with extraterrestrials through the CE5 protocols. 

In the next episode, we explore details of Unacknowledged Special Access Programs (USAPs).

Dr. Steven Greer is the founding father of the Disclosure Project, The Center for the Study of Extraterrestrial Intelligence, and creator of the CE5 Contact protocol.

title: The Unacknowledged Threat
body:
Bringing insight into the secretive black operations known as Unacknowledged Special Access Projects (USAPs), Dr. Steven Greer reveals their unprecedented power due to unlimited funding and lack of governmental oversight. He sheds light on these hidden programs and those involved, the advanced technologies they have access to, and the lengths they’ll go to in order to keep the world dependent on the centralized petrodollar economy.
 
In the next episode, Dr. Greer brings to light the forces against Contact and Disclosure.

title: Dangers to The Missions
body:
Astonishing experiences at CE5 events quickly caught the attention of the intelligence community in the early 1990s. During that time, Dr. Steven Greer released the Disclosure Project Briefing document to government officials. 

Clandestine forces opposing open contact with extraterrestrial intelligences, targeted Dr. Greer's team with Directed Energy Weapons (DEWs). He shares the hardships, dangers, and meaningful connections that have strengthened his mission to unite humanity in peace and love.
 
In this next episode, we will gain a greater understanding of Consciousness technology.

body:
In the not-too-distant future, technology will interface with human consciousness, according to Dr. Steven Greer. Dr. Greer discusses how the CE5 coherent thought sequencing allows humans and ET intelligences to communicate instantaneously, beyond time and space. 

In the next episode we explore how humans can become part of the greater galactic community.

body:
More people around the world are learning to make contact with extraterrestrial intelligences. As this evolves, we will gain a greater understanding of our place amongst the intergalactic community. In the next episode, we discover the differences between disclosure and disinformation, as Dr. Greer details how humanity needs to strive for peace in order to survive, and in turn, evolve.

title: Who's Controlling the Disclosure Narrative?
body:
As Disclosure gains traction, how will the "Empire" strike back? Dr. Steven Greer speaks with Billy Carson to discuss the evolution of Disclosure and the need for a peaceful revolution.

Exploring recent revelations in the media and how mainstream disinformation is attempting to co-opt Disclosure, Dr. Greer suggests how a “fake alien invasion” staged by shadow governments would intentionally divide, disrupt, and distract humanity from the essential goal of peace.
 
In the next episode, Dr. Greer further explains how a peaceful revolution is necessary for humanity to connect with cosmological consciousness and attain further evolution.

body:

In the next episode, Dr. Greer continues to elucidate on the power of peaceful revolution as humanity’s gateway to a conscious evolution.

title: The Delta of Change
body:
In the finale of our 10-part special Disclosure series, Dr. Greer expands on the necessity to reach lasting peace in order for higher beings to help connect humanity to our latent potential in the greater cosmos. 

As Dr. Greer puts it, matters of diplomacy with higher beings cannot be left to the military industrial complex. Rather, the world should unite around a nonviolent vision for the future focused on becoming a peaceful civilization. To usher in the delta of change we will need to implement free energy and real social justice to earn our place within the galactic community.
